		   Gopher VR Toolkit Source Release
                   --------------------------------

This is the source code for Gopher VR.

**********************************************************************
********************     I M P O R T A N T !      ********************
You will need to make a symbolic link to the regular Unix gopher
source tree like this:

  ln -s /home/arcwelder/lindner/gopherX_X_X ./gopher

**********************************************************************

libtracker/
    Audio tools for playing soundtracker/noisetracker modules

libvogl/
    Very Ordinary GL, a library for doing 3D fast

gophervr/
    Source code for GopherVR

lib/
    Where compiled libraries are installed

bin/
    Where compiled programs are installed



